org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory

Interface ItemStackSnapshot

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataSerializable, ImmutableDataHolder<ItemStackSnapshot>, ImmutableValueStore<ItemStackSnapshot,ImmutableDataManipulator<?,?>>, PropertyHolder, Translatable, ValueContainer<ItemStackSnapshot>

    public interface ItemStackSnapshot
extends ImmutableDataHolder<ItemStackSnapshot>, Translatable
    Represents a snapshot of an ItemStack as an ImmutableDataHolder to represent all of the data associated with the ItemStack of which the snapshot was created from. Being that it is a snapshot, a snapshot cannot be modified, but modifications will result in a new instance of the ItemStackSnapshot.
